The Telegraph - Calcutta (Kolkata) | Metro | The City Diary
                                                                                                               The City Diary
                Basudev Bag, the deputy inspector-general of police accused of torturing his minor help, has been asked to go on leave till the allegation is further reviewed, home secretary Ardhendu Sen said on Thursday. The decision came five days after the eight-year-old alleged she had been beaten up by the officer.					  quot; A case of physical abuse has been lodged with Sankrail police station... departmental action will follow soon, Sen added. The help, who was shifted to a Liluah home, was handed over to her father.  Cup telecast: The impasse between ESPN STAR Sports and MSO Manthan was resolved on Thursday, hours before the first match of the Super Eight stage in the ICC T20 World Cup.   Cell theft racket: Two boys in their early teens, hailing from Jharkhand, were arrested in the New Market area on Thursday on the charge of lifting cellphones. More than 15 phones were found on the two.   Body found: The body of Amirul Islam Sardar, 24, missing since Wednesday, was found in a pond near his house in Bankra Natunpara, Howrah, on Thursday evening. Sheikh Masud, a resident of the neighbourhood, has been arrested.   Doctor beaten: Tapas Bhattacharya, a 52-year-old doctor was beaten up on Thursday and his house in Garfa damaged following the death of a 22-year-old youth. Relatives blamed Samir Sahas death on medical negligence. Saha, who had been suffering from headache for the past 10 days. had undergone treatment under Bhattacharya in a Garfa clinic for a week before being shifted to Beleghata ID Hospital, where he died.  Diagnostic centres closed wo diagnostic centres in Salt Lake  at BF 87 and AD 71  were sealed on Thursday as they were allegedly being run without a licence.                                                                                                                                                                
